go-hardware-driver (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Generic driver for GOcontroll plug-in modules on Moduline controllers.
  * Reads /usr/lib/firmware/gocontroll/modules.json (schema v1.0).
  * Publishes input values and output feedback via /dev/shm/gocontroll/.
  * Implementations: input-6ch, output-6ch.
  * Stubs: input-10ch, input-4-20ma, output-10ch, bridge-2ch.
  * Pulse-counter / encoder reset support per channel.
  * 100 Hz fixed tick, sysinit.target start, CPUAffinity=3, Nice=-20.

 -- Rick Gijsberts <rickgijsberts@gocontroll.com>  Thu, 08 May 2026 09:00:00 +0200
